==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: necklace
<hw>neck"lace</hw> <pr>(?; 48)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
string of beads, etc., or any continuous band or chain, worn around the
neck as an ornament.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>A rope or chain fitted around the
masthead to hold hanging blocks for jibs and stays.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>necklaced</ent>⟦br⟧
